name: Recharging The Energy
description:
She's still and not moving doesn't mean she's constrained, but she's recharging her energy to act crazier than usual. because not everyone can act continuously, they also need to rest to fill their energy, so if you see someone else being silent, it doesn't mean he is giving up, please change your negative thoughts to other people with positive thoughts, because not everyone is like what they are you see now. 

1099 x 1518 px
